@page "/about"
@using ServiceStack.Mvc
@attribute [RenderStatic]
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About";
    ViewData["Description"] = "About sourceman - a programming blog by Magnus Kallman";
    Layout = "_Layout";
}

<div class="about-page content-narrow">
    <section class="about-hero">
        <h1>About</h1>
        <p>
            Hi, I'm Magnus — a freelancing senior software engineer, cloud architect, and professional
            problem solver. Working in software since 2012, mostly around the Microsoft
            .NET stack and Azure.
            I care deeply about my trade and the users of my software.
        </p>
        <br/>
        <p>
            I'm a nerd. When I'm not coding, I'm probably gardening, sport climbing,
            reading a book, or fermenting something.
        </p>
        <br/>
        <p>
            I occasionally write about my side-projects and blog posts related to software engineering on this site. 
        </p>
    </section>

    <blockquote class="about-quote">
        Software performance <em>is still</em> one of the most overlooked features.
    </blockquote>

    <div class="about-grid">
        <p>Below is a selection from my career, where I have worked primarily with web technologies on the backend — building e-commerce platforms, bespoke web applications, APIs, data synchronization tools, and much more.</p>
        <section class="about-column">
            <h2 class="about-heading">Industries</h2>
            <ul class="about-list">
                <li>Retail</li>
                <li>Food retail</li>
                <li>Book &amp; publishing</li>
                <li>Restaurant wholesale</li>
                <li>EV charging infrastructure</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="about-column">
            <h2 class="about-heading">Expertise</h2>
            <ul class="about-list">
                <li>Microsoft Azure</li>
                <li>.NET</li>
                <li>Go</li>
                <li>Rust</li>
                <li>Cloud architecture</li>
                <li>Code performance reviews</li>
                <li>Advanced troubleshooting — memory leaks, hot paths</li>
                <li>Agentic development</li>
                <li>Harness Engineering</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
    </div>

    <section class="about-links">
        <h2 class="about-heading">Where to find me</h2>
        <ul class="link-list">
            <li>
                <a href="https://github.com/magkal" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a>
                <span class="link-handle">@@magkal</span>
            </li>
            <li>
                <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/magnus-k%C3%A4llman-976167114/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a>
                <span class="link-handle">Magnus Källman</span>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </section>
</div>
